Review_Text: 1. "Break through the noise - focus on one thing to the extreme, and stop one thing".2. The Guate-amala project is truly inspirational.3. Intrigued by the "Small, Medium, Large, Extra Large" book.

Beautiful visuals and very inspiring and moving documentary for every designer. The way Mau talks and thinks about design is quite unusual. Made me think of design in a completely different way!10/10.
